WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:19.720
For a hundred thousand years, humans have looked up at the night sky and wondered about

00:19.720 --> 00:22.160
those awesome points of light.

00:22.160 --> 00:23.160
What are they?

00:23.160 --> 00:24.300
What are they made of?

00:24.300 --> 00:26.480
How did they get there?

00:26.480 --> 00:31.100
They didn't have the technology to find out, so they guessed that magical beings had created

00:31.100 --> 00:32.280
it all.

